{"type": "article", "id": 21123, "title": "橡木家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-22T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071223135jeCYXv9mSNPpnD2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国的设计工作室 big-game 为日本家具生产商 Karimoku 设计的家具系列。包括长椅，边桌和茶几。家具的主要结构使用了小直径的橡木，让原本厚重的木材料显得轻盈，同时拥有结实的特征，适合年轻人。桌子有几种不同型号，结构同样简单，4 根木腿与桌面垂直，整体是对称，很优雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071223113V6Gxpfc71nFONrK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122311utJrwT0kjMQXBysq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122312jLivWMBCI3THJoe0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122312OelD5CgI08r3j4pY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}